What we made in a month back in Feb… we’re now doing in one day.

Still trying to process that.

There were days we kept refreshing the dashboard, hoping for even one more order to come in.
From Oct to Feb — it felt like we were just stuck on repeat. Same numbers. Same doubts.

But May?
May changed something.

This one’s special. Not just because the numbers grew… but because they reminded me why we started GOAT Life in the first place.
To build something that actually works. Something people want to come back to.

Still a long way to go but for now, this feels like a quiet win we’ll always remember.
Grateful to everyone who’s been a part of this. Let’s keep going.

We are not GoOAT now,

Yes, we’ve changed our name but not our mission.

We started as GoOAT, with a focus on oats that are ridiculously tasty, healthy, and convenient.
But as we grew, we realized our vision was much bigger.

We’re not just building a brand around oats ,
We’re building a brand around how people can make their food more convenient and less time-consuming.
Because eating healthy shouldn’t be boring and difficult 

That’s why we’re now GOAT LIFE 
a brand that reflects our bigger mission: to simplify healthy living for people like you and us.

This is just the beginning.
